<plot>Kath will go to great lengths to find the perfect bubbly bathtub to rant about what's troubling her world. And what's a rant without a rave? Each webisode is shot from the sanctity of her bubble bath. Bathroom regulars include: "Paul in the Hall" (a guy with no opinion), "Pete on the Seat" (a no-nonsense fellow who articulates from the toilet), "The Little Man in the Boat" (a tiny man with big life experiences) and "Funky the Monkey" (a fur ball that has Kath's back). Plus, every webisode will feature a special guest... in the bath with Kath.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262816</url></doc>
